Data attribution

This code analyzes the genome-scale CD4+ T-cell Perturb-seq dataset of
Zhu R., Dann E. et al. (2025), "Genome-scale perturb-seq in primary human CD4+
T cells maps context-specific regulators of T cell programs and human immune
traits" (bioRxiv), distributed via the CZI Virtual Cells Platform. That dataset
and its companion analysis repository are the property of their authors and are
governed by their own licenses and terms of use. The MIT license above applies
to the code in this repository, not to the source dataset.
